o class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/677240/extras/a0cb951bc6de721a6ff480ba51d28e46.poster.avif?t=1507408388\" width=516 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/677240/extras/a0cb951bc6de721a6ff480ba51d28e46.webm?t=1507408388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/677240/extras/a0cb951bc6de721a6ff480ba51d28e46.mp4?t=1507408388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your character</h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/677240/extras/4c1df4c82f7e1400b3e5cfbb9996c89e.apng?t=1507408388\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/677240/extras/4c1df4c82f7e1400b3e5cfbb9996c89e.poster.avif?t=1507408388\" class=\"bb_img\" width=132 height=37 /></picture></span><br><br>Level up and <strong>get new skills</strong>, and collect money to <strong>purchase upgrades for your weapons</strong>, and other items at the Andy's stores scattered across the city -if you find them.",
